        <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
             HOW TO ADD A NEW RELEASE:
             1. Archive → export NarraC.app from Xcode
             2. Zip it:
                  ditto -c -k --sequesterRsrc --keepParent NarraC.app NarraC-X.Y.zip
             3. Get the signature + byte length:
                  PATH_TO_SPARKLE/bin/sign_update NarraC-X.Y.zip
             4. Create a GitHub Release at github.com/natsukaze-soft/narrac-updates
                Upload the .zip as a release asset
             5. Copy the asset download URL into sparkle:url below
             6. Update version, shortVersionString, pubDate, sparkle:edSignature, length
             7. Commit and push this file — GitHub Pages serves it automatically
             ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

        <item>
